- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses synthesis of schedulers for components. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with interactive systems and Markov chains. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper discusses a specification formalism for IMC. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper presents algorithms for compositional verification and optimization.
